09/06/2010
ANKARA, Turkey -- Police have arrested 17 people suspected of ties to the al-Qaeda terrorist group, local media reported on Wednesday (June 9th).
According to the reports, simultaneous raids were conducted on Tuesday in four cities across the country, most in the central city of Konya.
(Hurriyet, AFP - 09/06/10;
AP, Anadolu news agency - 08/06/10)
